post.description:
Create all Work Locations on that partrevision:
build_order & place_in_line are both required fields.

location body should look like this:
{
"locations":[
{
"location_external_key":"two",
"build_order":1,
"operations":[
{
"operation_external_key":"1hr", // OR:
"operation_id":1,
"repetitions":5,
"setup":true,
"place_in_line":1,
"instructions": [{
"instruction": "do the thing better"
}
]
},
]
}
]
}

